<tableCitation box="[596,681,726,753]" captionStart="TABLE 5" captionStartId="25.[151,239,527,553]" captionTargetPageId="25" captionText="TABLE 5. Karyotype data of genus Hylaeamys. Species, diploid (2n) and fundamental (FN) numbers, collection localities, geographic coordinates and reference." pageId="24" pageNumber="25">Table 5</tableCitation>
